# Insect on Yellow Paper

Modular CV scaffold with three interchangeable approaches:
- YOLO (Ultralytics)
- RT-DETR style transformer detector
- Classical CV baseline (thresholding + connected components)

## Quickstart
```
pip install -e .
insect list-approaches
insect prepare-data --project insect_yellow --approach yolo --config configs/yolo.yaml
insect train --project insect_yellow --approach yolo --config configs/yolo.yaml
insect evaluate --project insect_yellow --approach yolo --config configs/yolo.yaml
insect predict --project insect_yellow --approach yolo --config configs/yolo.yaml --image data/raw/insect_yellow/images/example.jpg
```

## Data layout
- Raw images: `data/raw/<project>/images`
- Processed datasets: `data/processed/<project>/<format>` (coco, yolo)
- Runs: `runs/<project>/<approach>/<timestamp>`
